      <title>布朗兄弟哈里曼银行总裁温辛表示，美国不会陷入经济衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/there-s-no-recession-coming-says-win-thin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布朗兄弟哈里曼全球市场研究主管温·辛 (Win Thin) 表示，现在还不是恐慌的时候。他说，今年美国不会出现经济衰退，经济“状况良好”。他正在接受“彭博监测”节目采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/there-s-no-recession-coming-says-win-thin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋新一轮打击影子舰队行动 禁止悬挂斯威士兰国旗的船只入港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uae-bans-eswatini-flagged-ships-in-fresh-shadow-fleet-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国禁止悬挂非洲内陆国家斯威士兰国旗的船只抵达，这是该中东国家与帮助运输俄罗斯石油供应的危险船只划清界限的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uae-bans-eswatini-flagged-ships-in-fresh-shadow-fleet-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街工程师发明了一种令人眼花缭乱的期权交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/wall-street-engineers-invent-a-new-head-spinning-options-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了搭上衍生品热潮的顺风车，金融奇才们可能已经想出了迄今为止最令人眼花缭乱的产品：芝加哥期权交易所 (Cboe) 全球市场公司 (Cboe Global Markets Inc.) 准备提供基于另一个指数期权的指数期货期权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/wall-street-engineers-invent-a-new-head-spinning-options-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:37:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度家庭预计未来几个月通胀将加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-coming-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行的一项调查显示，印度家庭预计未来三个月至一年内通胀将加速，主要受食品价格、住房和服务成本的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-coming-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
