      <title>沃尔格林开始发售首批 6 亿美元垃圾债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/walgreens-kicks-off-600-million-sale-of-first-junk-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃博联 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 已开始营销其首只高收益债券，筹集资金以偿还 11 月到期的票据。]]></description>
